User Input Notes

  
  Send Raw Input    |    Send Commands

1.  Saves traffic        1. No need for onclick detection

2. Ability usage would
   be send as commands(
   Including hotkeys)

3. Adds delay between
   user input and server
   dection of the input
   (not result of input)


Sending commands:
  -Send selection command(array of selected unit ids)
  -Send move command(world point, affects existing selection of units)
  -Send attack command(world point or unit, affects existing selection of units)
  -Send ability command(id and target id/target world point, building produce orders are considered abilities)